Message: When will the construction start and what is the expected completion date?
Reply: Construction will start in August 2024 with expected completion by December 2026.

Message: Are there any nearby schools within walking distance?
Reply: Yes there are 2 primary schools and 1 secondary school within 1km radius.

Message: What amenities will be available in the development?
Reply: The development will include a playground swimming pool gym and multipurpose hall.

Message: Is there sufficient parking for residents?
Reply: Yes each unit is allocated one parking space with additional visitor parking available.

Message: How far is the nearest MRT station?
Reply: The nearest MRT station is 400m away approximately a 5-minute walk.

Message: What is the expected maintenance fee for a 4-room flat?
Reply: The expected monthly maintenance fee is $45-$60 depending on the exact unit.

Message: Is there a playground for children in the development?
Reply: Yes there will be a children's playground and a small garden area.

Message: What is the orientation of the executive flats?
Reply: The executive flats are north-south oriented to minimize direct sunlight exposure.

Message: Are pets allowed in the development?
Reply: Yes pets are allowed but subject to HDB regulations on pet ownership.

Message: How many lifts are there per block?
Reply: Each block is served by 2 lifts to ensure minimal waiting time.

Message: Is there a BBQ area in the development?
Reply: Yes there will be designated BBQ pits that residents can book for gatherings.

Message: Are the flats designed with eco-friendly features?
Reply: Yes all units have energy-efficient lighting water-saving fixtures and good natural ventilation.
